    rating: "Pretty Bad"
    comments: "The concept is pretty interesting as the \'Lights Out\' concept combines paranormal tropes with \'asylum\' tropes; the plot structure is not that great because the runtime is too short, so there isn\'t enough runway to lay out a holistic story; the character writing uses stereotypical paranormal, insane tropes"
  }
  screenplay {
