  pacing: "Pacing is too fast as the runtime is just too short (there really is only 2-3 plot points); they could have added 15 minutes to help support the movie"
  climax: "Climax has good horror elements (but the conflict resolution is incredibly forced)"
  tone: "Tone is paranormal/insane horror"
  final_notes: ""
  overall: "Overall, a paranormal horror movie that does a pretty good job at eliciting fear through an interesting concept and jump scares; but there just isn\'t enough runtime to make this a holistic story"
